act.article:
2 Definitions. 

1 In these rules, unless the context 
otherwise requires, 

 a Act means the Food Safety and Standards Act, 2006 (34 of 2006); 
 b Authority means the Food Safety and Standards Authority of India 
  established under sub-section (1) of section 4 of the Act; 
 c Chairperson means the Chairperson of the Authority; 
 d meeting means a meeting convened by the Authority; 
 e Member means a member of the Authority. 

2 All other words and expressions used herein but not defined shall have 
the meanings respectively assigned to them in the Act.
